Design Patterns Used:
Factory Pattern - Person hierarchy (Customer/Admin/FrontDeskOfficer)

Strategy Pattern - Search interface with Catalog implementation

State Pattern - BookingStatus, PaymentStatus enums

Composite Pattern - Cinema → CinemaHall → CinemaHallSeat hierarchy

Observer Pattern - Notification system for bookings


Core Functionalities:
User Management - Customer, Admin, FrontDeskOfficer accounts

Movie & Show Management - Add movies, create shows

Cinema Management - Halls, seats, and locations

Search System - Movie search by multiple criteria

Booking System - Seat selection and payment processing

Payment Processing - Transaction management

Seat Management - Seat reservation and availability